#ddev-generated
## Supabase DDEV Addon Configuration
## Copied to .ddev/supabase/.env on first install.
## WARNING: Do not commit .ddev/supabase/.env to version control.
##
## When you change POSTGRES_PASSWORD:
##   1. Update POSTGRES_PASSWORD below
##   2. Update all lines containing "your-super-secret-and-long-postgres-password" below
##   3. Update DATABASE_URL in docker-compose.supabase.yaml (supavisor service)
##   4. Run: ddev restart

############
# Database
# POSTGRES_HOST is overridden in docker-compose to "supabase-db"
############
